{"tid":2269914,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被起訴阻差辦公及拒捕 浸大學生記者鄧澤旻：警砌我生豬肉","createTime":"2020-11-03T17:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T10:48:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"469446098c237cdc14e7efafe04d746114f598b0","tid":2269914,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"去年11月在太古城中心採訪時，被警方拘捕兼恐嚇雞姦的浸大學生會編輯委員會記者鄧澤旻，被警方落案起訴，指控他今年5月於中環ifc商場「和你Lunch」期間，阻差辦公及拒捕。<br />\n<br />\n鄧澤旻表示，早前因公眾地方行為不檢及拒捕被捕，昨日須前往中區警署報到，結果被警方正式落案起訴阻差辦公及拒捕，案件將於本周五在東區裁判法院提堂。警方只着他簽署文件，沒有解釋更改罪名的理由。他續說，下午收到港台員工被捕消息，已預料自己亦將被正式落案起訴，認為警方因找不到證據，「就夾硬話我係假記者，砌我生豬肉」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/6IM3Y3TT2NDTVF4UTP35ZATS4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2F6IM3Y3TT2NDTVF4UTP35ZATS4E%2F&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo2Hyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=8a30cbcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2F6IM3Y3TT2NDTVF4UTP35ZATS4E%2F&h=7bdd221d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/6IM3Y3TT2NDTVF4UTP35ZATS4E/</a>"},{"pid":"c62ecdc8d86f3d4ce756e30fd7cab5cd9a93dd8b","tid":2269914,"uid":59357,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4947be22873b146f632c12b4aadf46d0e1348e75","tid":2269914,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c4045769bd588a0d81b6beda173d97e9e99de3","tid":2269914,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"死黑警 又想雞姦𡃁仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 